 Pet Spa\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about All Four Paws Pet Spa.  What makes this dog facility special is its wonderful, great, professional. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. four paws or sherry the owner is a wonderful person and my maltipoo loves her, she has groomed him for years, best groomer ever was This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (423) 926-4874. \",\"slug\":\"all-four-paws-pet-spa\",\"address\":\"2890 Boones Creek Rd\",\"street\":\"2890 Boones Creek Rd\",\"city\":\"Johnson City\",\"state\":\"TN\",\"zipCode\":\"37615\",\"full_address\":\"2890 Boones Creek Rd, Johnson City, TN 37615, USA\",\"latitude\":36.38314769999999,\"longitude\":-82.4203892,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJG5T5bzqIWogRuEuEaPB4Frs\",\"phone\":\"(423) 926-4874\",\"website\":\"\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.7,\"reviewCount\":73,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"Closed\",\"Tuesday\":\"8:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"8:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"8:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"8:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"8:00 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"Closed\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJgzyQLAmJWogRWRQVKWcl1Uo\",\"name\":\"Bed and Biscuit\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Bed and Biscuit has become a favorite among the area residents.  What makes this dog facility special is its friendly, attentive, clean. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. the staff was friendly and attentive and sent updates and even called to ask questions before they tried something new with our dog This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (423) 427-6226. Visit their website at https://bcbedandbiscuit.com/?utm_source=cumulus&utm_medium=onlinepresence&utm_campaign=gbp to learn more about their services and pricing.\",\"slug\":\"bed-and-biscuit\",\"address\":\"1762 Old Gray Station Rd\",\"street\":\"1762 Old Gray Station Rd\",\"city\":\"Johnson City\",\"state\":\"TN\",\"zipCode\":\"37615\",\"full_address\":\"1762 Old Gray Station Rd, Johnson City, TN 37615, USA\",\"latitude\":36.3839472,\"longitude\":-82.41302999999999,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJgzyQLAmJWogRWRQVKWcl1Uo\",\"phone\":\"(423) 427-6226\",\"website\":\"https://bcbedandbiscuit.com/?utm_source=cumulus&utm_medium=onlinepresence&utm_campaign=gbp\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.3,\"reviewCount\":76,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"6:30 AM – 6:30 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"6:30 AM – 6:30 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"6:30 AM – 6:30 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"6:30 AM – 6:30 PM\",\"Friday\":\"6:30 AM – 6:30 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"8:00 AM – 6:30 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"Closed\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJSev21z2IWogRgtnHN4l3XRA\",\"name\":\"Boones Creek Animal Hospital\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Boones Creek Animal Hospital.  What makes this veterinary care special is its clean, caring, great. The staff's dedication to c